  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p class="p1"><span class="s1">Book any <strong>Tour</strong> featured in our Inghams Lakes &amp; Mountains 2019 or Inghams Italy 2019 brochure and claim your free half case of wine.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">1. </span><span class="s4"></span><span class="s1">This offer is for new bookings only,  from January 2019 - 31st March 2019 for 2019 <strong>Tours</strong>.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">2. </span><span class="s1">There is no cash </span><span class="s2">or other </span><span class="s1">alternative.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">3. </span><span class="s1">One half-case of wine containing 6 bottles will be sent for each new booking for any <strong>Tour</strong> featured in our Inghams Lakes &amp; Mountains 2019 or Inghams Italy 2019 brochures.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">4.</span><span class="s4"> </span><span class="s1">Offer is open to UK residents aged 18 or over</span><span class="s2"> only</span><span class="s1">.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">5.</span><span class="s4"> </span><span class="s1">This offer cannot be used in conjunction with any other offer.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">6.</span><span class="s4"> </span><span class="s1">Once your booking is </span><span class="s2">confirmed</span><span class="s1">, <strong>please email <a href="mailto:wine@inghams.co.uk"><span class="s6">wine@inghams.co.uk</span></a></strong> with your name, booking reference and </span><span class="s2">UK </span><span class="s1">delivery address</span><span class="s5"> </span><span class="s2">to claim your free half-case of wine</span><span class="s1">. </span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">7.</span><span class="s4"> </span><span class="s1">The wine will be delivered in April/May 2019 by our supplier Laithwaites Wine.  If you book via a Travel Agent the wine will be sent to them and it will be their responsibility to then pass the wine on to you.  No responsibility can be taken for your Travel Agent not passing this on to you.</span></p>
<p class="p1"><span class="s1">8.</span><span class="s4"> </span><span class="s1">Inghams reserve the right to remove </span><span class="s2">or amend </span><span class="s1">this offer at any time without notice.</span></p>]]></bodyText>
